{"tid":1453462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報 : 「黑色恐怖」席捲香港","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:25:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2aed12946e7b6b655d17f683e85f8402b2680d44","tid":1453462,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:16:10.000Z","msg":"《人民日報》海外版發表評論文章，指非法集結的極端激進分子，昨晚在香港多地向警察投擲汽油彈，導致一名警員嚴重燒傷，暴力一再升級，惡行突破底線，席捲香港的「黑色恐怖」，正呈愈演愈烈之勢，此刻必須力挺香港警隊，因為挺警隊就是挺法治、挺香港安寧和挺市民利益。<br />\n<br />\n文章以《香港阿Sir，撐你到底》為題，指香港警方無愧於世界上最優秀警隊的讚譽，但正遭遇輿論的不公對待。文章提到，內外反華勢力的口誅筆伐，污蔑警方暴力執法，反對派媒體和外國記者的攝像機鏡頭，只拍警察與示威者對峙，卻不拍暴徒襲警等。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，香港不能再亂下去，止暴制亂、恢復秩序是當務之急，重申中央旗幟鮮明支持警隊嚴正執法。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474122-20190812.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474122-20190812.htm&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=2139893b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474122-20190812.htm&h=4c0fd1f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474122-20190812.htm</a>"},{"pid":"92c2bf745de35ce7fc8ec3025b6c4c7f74f81e08","tid":1453462,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:21:10.000Z","msg":"白色恐怖卷香港！！！死返大陸啦"},{"pid":"e79c270123c8d75dfc4fdb210d5e42b784b6e9c1","tid":1453462,"uid":270778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58db9966fd91ff2d336f2f02a40b0c9876e32e8","tid":1453462,"uid":42982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"You ask for it"}]}